txt.en: Ancient moon-letters are waiting to be uncovered by those who brave the long forgotten halls, deep within the Pit of Stonejaws.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Stonejaws: Leader of the Frost to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>

The scout gives you a missive to collect moon-letters.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Stonejaws: Leader of the Frost to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
